@startuml
title UC02 — User registers/logs in/resets password/OAuth Google — Sequence
actor "Guest" as Actor
participant "AuthPage" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "AuthService" as AuthService
database "MySQL" as DB
participant "Google OAuth" as Google_OAuth
participant "Resend" as Resend
Actor -> UI : submit authentication request
UI -> API : HTTPS request
API -> AuthService : route and authorize
AuthService -> DB : read/write User
DB -->> AuthService : data result
AuthService -> Google_OAuth : integration request
Google_OAuth -->> AuthService : integration response
AuthService -> Resend : integration request
Resend -->> AuthService : integration response
AuthService -->> API : response
API -->> UI : JSON result
UI -->> Actor : account/session is created or reset email is sent
@enduml
